title: Recall Notification Report 065-2015 (Turkey and Beef)
summary: WASHINGTON, April 20, 2015 Michigan Brand, Inc., a Bay City, Mich. establishment, is recalling approximately 737 pounds of turkey and beef products due to misbranding, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS) announced today.
